    "wpWinPosId": 2,
    "wsWinStyleId": 2
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 221551,
    "dDurationMs": 3971,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "probably with no effect other\nthan an initial vague flu like illness."
    } ],
    "wpWinPosId": 5,
    "wsWinStyleId": 2
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 226323,
    "dDurationMs": 3570,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "But even though the parasite may not\ncause immediate problems in normal,"
