    "wpWinPosId": 3,
    "wsWinStyleId": 2
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 253450,
    "dDurationMs": 4838,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "So why have I chosen to spend my career\nresearching this parasite of cats"
